{
  "stem": "1765.2",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 15.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Compared to trains going to Treblinka or to Auschwitz, it was fine.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But people were squeezed on these [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They were like, you know, platform beds.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We slept like sardines, but we didn't have to stand.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Everything is relative.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I knew the war was going on, but a war that isn't in your backyard is a very amorphous thing.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It's just-- it's happening somewhere, but it doesn't really touch you.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But once I got in that cattle car, I knew what war was, because that, for me, was war.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, we got some watery soup, and bread.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And when we stopped at various stops, people were coming to sell things, you know, peasants.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we had no windows.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There were just small openings on the top [INAUDIBLE], on the top platform where people slept.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And people who had money could buy sometimes a piece of cheese or bread or whatever.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But there were peasants.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "There wasn't just rich people in our-- in our echelon car.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "There were peasants, and they brought food.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And they actually offered it to those who didn't bring any food.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But my mother would never accept any.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Wouldn't let me, not that I would do it without her permission.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So we got to Siberia after six weeks, and we were put on the marketplace [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] like slaves.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Just around the marketplace, like an open square where, on-- on Sundays people sold stuff in stands and barrels and whatever.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And people were just placed around it with our bags or-- or suitcases.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And people came around and looked at us, like-- you know, the only thing is I said to someone, they didn't look at our mouths, whether our teeth were all right.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "It was like a slave market.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
